title: Eight Immortals Vegetarian - Pasir Panjang
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Fast food, Take-out
description: Food stall inside Kopitiam, located at Pasir Panjang Wholesale Centre which is next to West Coast Car Mart and a 5-minute walk from Haw Par Villa MRT station. Serves rice, bee hoon, noodles with a variety of vegetables and mock meats.
streetAddress: Blk 1 Pasir Panjang Road 01-02 Pasir Panjang Wholesale Centre
